import { createStitches } from '@stitches/react';

export const {
	styled,
	css,
	globalCss,
	keyframes,
	getCssText,
	theme,
	createTheme,
	config,
} = createStitches({
	media: {
		'bp1': '(min-width: 640px and min-height: 960px)',
		'bp2': '(min-width: 960px and min-height: 1440px)',
		'bp3': '(min-width: 1920px and min-height: 2880px)',
		'bp4': '(min-width: 2400px and min-height: 3600px)',
		'bg-bp1': '(max-width: 640px and max-height: 960px)',
		'bg-bp2': '(max-width: 960px and max-height: 1440px)',
		'bg-bp3': '(max-width: 1440px and max-height: 2160px)',
		'width-bp1': '(min-width: 640px)',
		'width-bp2': '(min-width: 960px)',
		'width-bp3': '(min-width: 1440px)',
		'width-bp4': '(min-width: 1920px)',
		'width-bp5': '(min-width: 2400px)',
		'height-bp1': '(min-height: 960px)',
		'height-bp2': '(min-height: 1440px)',
		'height-bp3': '(min-height: 2160px)',
		'height-bp4': '(min-height: 2880px)',
		'height-bp5': '(min-height: 3600px)',
	},
});
